'''ribose'''
{{wikipedia}}
# {{biochemistry}} A naturally occurring [[pentose]] [[sugar]], which is a component of the [[nucleoside]]s and [[nucleotide]]s that comprise the [[nucleic acid]] [[biopolymer]], [[RNA]]. It is also found in [[riboflavin]].

